cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and understanding.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a framework for learning representations for robots to reason over both motions and intermediate goals implied by human instructions.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is another likely category as the paper focuses on executing natural language commands on a robot in simulated scenes.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a framework for learning representations.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also a possible category as the paper deals with interpreting natural language commands for a robot in simulated scenes, which may involve computer vision techniques.
